Change Email:
	-User would have to be currently logged in to access the opportunity to change their email
	-New confirmation email sent if:
		-New email entered is unique (not being used) and is of valid format
	-Email not sent if:
		-New email is in use or invalid format
	-If user clicks on reconfirm email, user should be updated and stay logged in
		-If logged out should they be able to change email?
			-Yes, but they must log in
